Derek Dubner - Boca Raton, Florida, Florida State University College of Law, Pennsylvania State University | about.meDerek DubnerCo-CEO in Boca Raton, FloridaDerek DubnerCo-CEO in Boca Raton, FloridaVisit my websiteAs co-CEO of IDI, Inc., Derek Dubner frames the business concept and strategy for an information solutions provider engaged in the data fusion sector. He oversees capital allocation for the company, which combines a large data archive with state-of-the-art systems architecture to deliver intelligence usable for such purposes as risk assessment, authentication, and fraud prevention. Along with rendering risk management services for clients ranging from government and law enforcement agencies to financial services and legal firms, Derek Dubner and IDI offer cross-functional technologies that produce unparalleled consumer data insights to facilitate precise marketing analytics.Previously, as a lawyer, Derek Dubner provided a small group of extremely wealthy clients with legal counsel concerning their business enterprises. He maintains an interest in the study of broad economic cycles and, as an active stock market investor, conducts his own research into the status of individual companies and entire industries.#investment#economics#technologyEducationFlorida State University College of LawPennsylvania State University


